- Implement static & dynamic crypto puzzles from S/Kademlia paper
- Genenerate ed25519 key pairs
- Describe changes to message headers & payload formats to add signatures,
  checksums, timestamps (to avoid replay attacks), etc.
- Want to encrypt data values when sending to nodes? Too expensive if storing
  10gb values on the network
